                    <p class="text-justify">Her treatment methods include deep tissue massage, myofascial release and trigger point therapy. She has a special interest in sports &amp; injury rehabilitation as well as pregnancy massage. Melodie is very passionate about her work and likes to tailor each session to the individual needs of her clients.</p>
                    <p class="text-justify">Melodie is an avid runner, completed two half marathons with hopes to finish a full marathon in the near future. Her weekends are spent running, hiking, biking, and climbing.</p>
